        Create a new KuduSession for applying write operations.

        Parameters
        ----------
        flush_mode : {'manual', 'sync', 'background'}, default 'manual'
          See Session.set_flush_mode
        timeout_ms : int, default 5000
          Timeout in milliseconds

        Returns
        -------
        session : kudu.Session
        """
